			<a href="./download/file.php?id=12015&amp;mode=view"><img src="./download/file.php?id=12015&amp;t=1" alt="Sonic 3 - Solda - S.png" /></a><br />
			<span class="gensmall">Sonic 3 - Solda - S.png [ 1.3 MiB | Viewed 1927 times ]</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br />Better resolution <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Y8Ynqcxbz4Isbej7Dj2qEhST-Jo6NqRj" class="postlink">here</a> and <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=130czNeMPUBKGCJn5Qw9xNcX2aZaozWjw" class="postlink">here</a>.<br />Oh, and I noticed I forgot to take a picture of the assembled board. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":-(" title="Sad" /><br />But I found a similar one <a href="http://elektropage.ru/cartmod/PCB_SRAM_1.jpg" class="postlink">here</a><br />If someone could please RE this board for me, I would be very happy. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" /><br /><br />Thanks in advance!

		

