	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I traced it out about a year ago.  It's not that complex.  Most of the functionality of the logic revolves around changing between sonic 3 mode as an individual cart, and sonic &amp; knuckles + sonic 3.  That gets controlled by B27 #RESET.  the S&amp;K grounds that pin permanently for the S3 cart.  Could be some errors with my schematic.  I only beeped out the interesting parts with a DMM.

		
